Below are the key files in this folder:

func_datapreprocessing : contains functions to preprocess the text on the recipe table
func_predict : contains the function to calculate vector similarity between query and recipe
func_similarityfunc : contains the equation to vector similarity
func_tfidf : contains function to vectorize text data 


main.py : the main py script to run the above-mentioned functions 


app.py :  contains the script to run Flask. It uses a local server to get user query and outputs a list of recipe recommendations. 
app.py needs to run with N.joblib, vectorized_corpus.joblib, and DF.joblib.
